---
layout: default
title: Alex's Tech Blog
---
%h1 Постчета :)
{% for post in site.posts %}
.post
  %h2
    %a{ :href => "{{ site.baseurl }}{{ post.url }}" } {{ post.title }}
  %p {{ post.content | strip_newlines | strip_html | truncatewords: 60 }}
  %span.date {{ post.date | date_to_string }}
  %a.readmore{ :href => "{{ site.baseurl }}{{ post.url }}" } Readmore →
{% endfor %}
